From: Project OS <project@example.com>
Date: Mon, 28 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] libmain: drop unavailable ostree sepolicy null-log call

Some OSTree versions do not provide ostree_sepolicy_set_null_log().
Drop the call for compatibility.

Signed-off-by: Project OS <project@example.com>
---
 src/app/libmain.cxx | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/src/app/libmain.cxx b/src/app/libmain.cxx
--- a/src/app/libmain.cxx
+++ b/src/app/libmain.cxx
@@ -489,7 +489,6 @@ early_main (void)
    * attached to a context object. */
   dnf_context_set_config_file_path ("");

-  ostree_sepolicy_set_null_log ();
 }

 // The C++ `main()`, invoked from Rust only for most CLI commands currently.
